Example 4 : Fold Expression (C++17)
=========================================================

Before C++17

Recursion required.

C++17 introduced Fold Expressions.

template<typename... Args>
auto sum(Args... args)
{
    return (... + args);
}

Usage

cout << sum(1,2,3,4);

Output

10

Very common interview question.

